{"id":235971,"date":"2024-01-31T11:52:53","date_gmt":"2024-01-31T06:22:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=235971"},"modified":"2024-01-31T12:12:44","modified_gmt":"2024-01-31T06:42:44","slug":"joe-dcruz","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/","title":{"rendered":"Joe D\u2019Cruz Wiki, Age, Wife, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-235972\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-.jpg\" alt=\"Joe D'Cruz\" width=\"601\" height=\"464\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-.jpg 727w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz--300x231.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 601px) 100vw, 601px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Joe D\u2019Cruz is a well-known Indian novelist, commercial shipping professional, and documentary filmmaker who has made significant contributions to Tamil cinema, Indian literature, and social welfare.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bcdfa2d17a5\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bcdfa2d17a5\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Family_Caste\" title=\"Family &amp; Caste\">Family &amp; Caste<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Parents_Siblings\" title=\"Parents &amp; Siblings\">Parents &amp; Siblings<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Wife_Children\" title=\"Wife &amp; Children\">Wife &amp; Children<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Other_Relatives\" title=\"Other Relatives\">Other Relatives<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Ship_Management\" title=\"Ship Management\">Ship Management<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Literary_Works\" title=\"Literary Works\">Literary Works<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Documentary_Films\" title=\"Documentary Films\">Documentary Films<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Social_Work\" title=\"Social Work\">Social Work<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#Awards\" title=\"Awards\">Awards<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/joe-dcruz\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>R. N. Joe D&#8217;Cruz <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_235971_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_235971_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/r-n-joe-d-cruz-b7b4492a\/?originalSubdomain=in\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Joe D&#8217;Cruz&#8217;s LinkedIn Account<\/a><\/span><\/span> was born in 1969 (<strong>age 54 years; as of 2023<\/strong>) in Village Uvari, district Tirunelveli in Tamil Nadu, India. He studied in the schools of the Uvari and Idaiyangudi villages. After completing his school education, he went to Loyola College in Chennai, Tamil Nadu to pursue an M.A. degree in Economics. Later, he received an M.Phil degree at St. Joseph&#8217;s College in Tiruchirapalli, Tamil Nadu.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Salt and Pepper<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-posing-with-a-ship.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-236027\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-posing-with-a-ship.jpg\" alt=\"Joe D'Cruz\" width=\"372\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-posing-with-a-ship.jpg 536w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-posing-with-a-ship-300x292.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 372px) 100vw, 372px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Caste\"><\/span>Family &amp; Caste<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Joe D&#8217;Cruz belongs to a &#8216;Roman Catholic Paravar,&#8217; in Uvari, a coastal village.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Not much is known about his parents.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236019\" style=\"width: 475px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-with-his-mother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236019\" class=\"size-full wp-image-236019\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-with-his-mother.jpg\" alt=\"Joe D\u2019Cruz with his mother\" width=\"465\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-with-his-mother.jpg 465w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-with-his-mother-300x248.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 465px) 100vw, 465px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236019\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Joe D\u2019Cruz with his mother<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wife_Children\"><\/span><strong>Wife &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>His wife&#8217;s name is Sasikala D&#8217;Cruz, and the couple has two children.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Other_Relatives\"><\/span><strong>Other Relatives<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>His grandfather&#8217;s name is Thomas Andrew.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ship_Management\"><\/span><strong>Ship Management<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Joe D\u2019Cruz joined the commercial shipping industry soon after completing his higher studies.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_235986\" style=\"width: 331px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-235986\" class=\" wp-image-235986\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu.jpg\" alt=\"A young Joe D'Cruz while working for a ship management company in Tamil Nadu\" width=\"321\" height=\"419\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu.jpg 471w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu-230x300.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-235986\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A young Joe D&#8217;Cruz while working for a ship management company in Tamil Nadu<\/p><\/div>\n<p>For more than three decades, he worked as the President of NTC Logistics Private Limited and Vice President of J.M. Baxi &amp; Company.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Literary_Works\"><\/span><strong>Literary Works<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In 2004, Joe D&#8217;Cruz published a book of Tamil poems titled \u2018Pulambazhkal.\u2019 His writings mostly talk about the history and lives of Parathavar fishermen in Tamil Nadu.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_235988\" style=\"width: 298px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-book-Pulambazhkal-by-Joe-DCruz.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-235988\" class=\" wp-image-235988\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-book-Pulambazhkal-by-Joe-DCruz.jpg\" alt=\"The cover of the book 'Pulambazhkal' by Joe D'Cruz\" width=\"288\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-book-Pulambazhkal-by-Joe-DCruz.jpg 247w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-book-Pulambazhkal-by-Joe-DCruz-194x300.jpg 194w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-235988\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The cover of the book &#8216;Pulambazhkal&#8217; by Joe D&#8217;Cruz<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In 2005, he released his novel \u2018Aazhi Soozh Ulagu,&#8217; which earned the Tamil Nadu State Government Literary Award and the Tamil Literary Garden Award. In this novel, he highlighted the lives of the fishermen who used catamarans and their conversion to Christianity.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_235989\" style=\"width: 295px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Aazhi-Soozh-Ulagu-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-235989\" class=\"size-full wp-image-235989\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Aazhi-Soozh-Ulagu-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz.jpg\" alt=\"The cover of the novel 'Aazhi Soozh Ulagu' by R. N. Joe D'Cruz\" width=\"285\" height=\"492\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Aazhi-Soozh-Ulagu-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz.jpg 285w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Aazhi-Soozh-Ulagu-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz-174x300.jpg 174w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 285px) 100vw, 285px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-235989\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The cover of the novel &#8216;Aazhi Soozh Ulagu&#8217; by R. N. Joe D&#8217;Cruz<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Joe D&#8217;Cruz&#8217;s novel &#8216;Korkai&#8217; was released in 2009 and won the Sahitya Akademi Award in 2013. The novel is based on the story of an ancient port city ruled by the Early Pandyan Kingdom. It focuses on the pearl and conch divers of the 20th-century community.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_235992\" style=\"width: 328px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Korkai-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-235992\" class=\"size-full wp-image-235992\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Korkai-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz.jpg\" alt=\"The cover of the novel 'Korkai' by R. N. Joe D'Cruz\" width=\"318\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Korkai-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz.jpg 318w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-cover-of-the-novel-Korkai-by-R.-N.-Joe-DCruz-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 318px) 100vw, 318px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-235992\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The cover of the novel &#8216;Korkai&#8217; by R. N. Joe D&#8217;Cruz<\/p><\/div>\n<p>His other literary works include Asthinapuram (2016), Verpiditha Vilai Nilangal (2017), Kavanam Thedum Kadaloram (2019), and Padaipugalin Uraiyadal (2020).<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documentary_Films\"><\/span><strong>Documentary Films<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>He made a documentary film &#8216;Vidiyatha Pozhuthukal&#8217; in 2008. In 2010, Joe D\u2019Cruz released another documentary named &#8216;Towards Dawn,&#8217; which primarily focused on the hardships faced by Tamil fishermen. He then scripted the dialogues for the Tamil movie &#8216;Maryan&#8217; in 2013.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_235998\" style=\"width: 351px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-poster-of-the-Tamil-film-Maryan-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-235998\" class=\"size-full wp-image-235998\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-poster-of-the-Tamil-film-Maryan-.jpg\" alt=\"The poster of the Tamil film 'Maryan'\" width=\"341\" height=\"492\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-poster-of-the-Tamil-film-Maryan-.jpg 341w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/The-poster-of-the-Tamil-film-Maryan--208x300.jpg 208w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 341px) 100vw, 341px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-235998\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The poster of the Tamil film &#8216;Maryan&#8217;<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Social_Work\"><\/span><strong>Social Work<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Joe D&#8217;Cruz is associated with a non-profit group Samskrita Bharati as its state president in Tamil Nadu. This group is dedicated to safeguarding the Sanskrit language.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236017\" style=\"width: 344px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Logo-of-Samskrita-Bharati-NGO.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236017\" class=\" wp-image-236017\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Logo-of-Samskrita-Bharati-NGO.jpg\" alt=\"Logo of Samskrita Bharati NGO\" width=\"334\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Logo-of-Samskrita-Bharati-NGO.jpg 406w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Logo-of-Samskrita-Bharati-NGO-283x300.jpg 283w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 334px) 100vw, 334px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236017\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Logo of Samskrita Bharati NGO<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In 2011, he voiced against the Kudankulam nuclear power project and stated reasons for its negative impact on the livelihoods of fishermen.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_235996\" style=\"width: 502px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-rally-organised-againt-the-establishment-of-the-Kudankulam-nuclear-power-project-in-2011-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-235996\" class=\"wp-image-235996 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-rally-organised-againt-the-establishment-of-the-Kudankulam-nuclear-power-project-in-2011-.jpg\" alt=\"A rally organised against the establishment of the Kudankulam nuclear power project in 2011\" width=\"492\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-rally-organised-againt-the-establishment-of-the-Kudankulam-nuclear-power-project-in-2011-.jpg 492w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-rally-organised-againt-the-establishment-of-the-Kudankulam-nuclear-power-project-in-2011--300x197.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 492px) 100vw, 492px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-235996\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A rally organised against the establishment of the Kudankulam nuclear power project in 2011<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He believes in the importance of improving existing ports in India rather than beginning new port projects. So, in 2017, he opposed the proposed &#8216;International Container Transhipment Terminal&#8217; at Enayam in Kanyakumari district in Tamil Nadu.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236004\" style=\"width: 582px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-march-against-the-International-Container-Transhipment-Terminal-at-Enayam-2017.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236004\" class=\"size-full wp-image-236004\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-march-against-the-International-Container-Transhipment-Terminal-at-Enayam-2017.jpg\" alt=\"A march against the 'International Container Transhipment Terminal' at Enayam (2017)\" width=\"572\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-march-against-the-International-Container-Transhipment-Terminal-at-Enayam-2017.jpg 572w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-march-against-the-International-Container-Transhipment-Terminal-at-Enayam-2017-300x188.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236004\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A march against the &#8216;International Container Transhipment Terminal&#8217; at Enayam (2017)<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In 2017, the Government of India appointed Joe D&#8217;Cruz as a member of the National Shipping Board in the Ministry of Shipping.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236009\" style=\"width: 489px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236009\" class=\" wp-image-236009\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu-.jpg\" alt=\"A young Joe D'Cruz while working for a ship management company in Tamil Nadu\" width=\"479\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu-.jpg 586w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/A-young-Joe-DCruz-while-working-for-a-ship-management-company-in-Tamil-Nadu--300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 479px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236009\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A young Joe D&#8217;Cruz while working for a ship management company in Tamil Nadu<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Joe D\u2019Cruz often supports Indian LGBTQA+ activist Gopi Shankar Madurai. He has worked on the advisory board of Srishti Madurai, a volunteer group for LGBTQA+ students.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Awards\"><\/span>Awards<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>2013:<\/strong> Sahitya Akademi Award for his novel &#8216;Korkai&#8217;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>2024:<\/strong> Padma Shri in the field of literature and education<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>During the 2014 Lok Sabha elections, Joe D&#8217;Cruz showed his support for BJP&#8217;s prime ministerial candidate, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Narendra Modi<\/a>, on his Facebook page. He faced threats and hate mail as a result. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_235971_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_235971_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/indianexpress.com\/article\/political-pulse\/celebrity-tamil-novelist-supports-narendra-modi-gets-threat\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Indian Express<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In that same year, he planned to translate his book &#8220;Aazhi Soozh Ulagu&#8221; from Tamil to English. However, the publisher, S. Anand, and the translator, V. Geetha, stopped the translation in response to Joe D&#8217;Cruz&#8217;s support for Modi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>After facing criticism from his peers, Joe D&#8217;Cruz clarified the reason for halting the book&#8217;s translation during a media discussion. He stated,<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>It is because of my opinion expressed on Facebook as Narendra Modi is the right choice for PM. I think their actions show the form of narrow mentality.\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>He criticized the Bharatiya Janata Party in 2017, blaming them for strengthening caste systems, Manu Smriti, and empowering violent political forces over beef consumption. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_235971_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_235971_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehindu.com\/news\/national\/tamil-nadu\/modi-govt-bolstering-caste-structure\/article19440502.ece\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Hindu<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Thereafter, Joe D&#8217;Cruz criticized Prime Minister <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Narendra Modi<\/a> for not helping the poor. He also disagreed with the BJP government&#8217;s plan for a &#8216;Maritime Container Terminal&#8217; at Enayam in Tamil Nadu, saying it would be like a natural disaster despite claims it&#8217;s a natural harbour.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>He supported the &#8216;Sampark Se Samarthan&#8217; (Contact for Support) program, which was led by PM <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/narendra-modi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Narendra Modi<\/a> in 2018.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_236012\" style=\"width: 474px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-supporting-the-Sampark-Se-Samarthan-Contact-for-Support-programme-2018.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236012\" class=\" wp-image-236012\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-supporting-the-Sampark-Se-Samarthan-Contact-for-Support-programme-2018.jpg\" alt=\"Joe D'Cruz while supporting the 'Sampark Se Samarthan' (Contact for Support) programme (2018)\" width=\"464\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-supporting-the-Sampark-Se-Samarthan-Contact-for-Support-programme-2018.jpg 607w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-supporting-the-Sampark-Se-Samarthan-Contact-for-Support-programme-2018-300x233.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 464px) 100vw, 464px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236012\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Joe D&#8217;Cruz while supporting the &#8216;Sampark Se Samarthan&#8217; (Contact for Support) programme (2018)<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Joe D\u2019Cruz likes smoking cigars on various occasions.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_236013\" style=\"width: 454px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-smoking-a-cigar.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236013\" class=\" wp-image-236013\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-smoking-a-cigar.jpg\" alt=\"Joe D'Cruz while smoking a cigar\" width=\"444\" height=\"230\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-smoking-a-cigar.jpg 533w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Joe-DCruz-while-smoking-a-cigar-300x155.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 444px) 100vw, 444px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236013\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Joe D&#8217;Cruz while smoking a cigar<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_235971_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_235971_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_minus_235971_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button collapsed\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_235971_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[\u2212]<\/span><\/p><\/div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container_235971_1\" class=\"collapsed\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">References<\/caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_235971_1_1\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>1<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/r-n-joe-d-cruz-b7b4492a\/?originalSubdomain=in\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Joe D&#8217;Cruz&#8217;s LinkedIn Account<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_235971_1_2\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>2<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/indianexpress.com\/article\/political-pulse\/celebrity-tamil-novelist-supports-narendra-modi-gets-threat\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Indian Express<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_235971_1_3\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>3<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehindu.com\/news\/national\/tamil-nadu\/modi-govt-bolstering-caste-structure\/article19440502.ece\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Hindu<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n <\/tbody> <\/table> <\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Joe D\u2019Cruz is a well-known Indian novelist, commercial shipping professional, and documentary filmmaker who has made significant contributions to Tamil cinema, Indian literature, and social welfare. Wiki\/Biography R. N. Joe D&#8217;Cruz Joe D&#8217;Cruz&#8217;s LinkedIn Account was born in 1969 (age 54 years; as of 2023) in Village Uvari, district Tirunelveli in Tamil Nadu, India. He studied in the schools of the Uvari and Idaiyangudi villages. After completing his school education, he went to Loyola College in Chennai, Tamil Nadu to pursue an M.A. degree in Economics. Later, he received an M.Phil degree at St. Joseph&#8217;s College in Tiruchirapalli, Tamil Nadu. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":41,"featured_media":235972,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[48],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/235971"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/41"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=235971"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/235971\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":236035,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/235971\/revisions\/236035"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/235972"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=235971"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=235971"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=235971"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}